fields.title: Eye Love 2 Stare (First Art Show)
fields.description:
To celebrate the summer and trying new things, Eye Love 2 Stare (Paul Simone & Alexsandra Star) presents our first ever art show at great new space, Playground on 1114 Bedford Ave.
Featuring:

Richard Perez - http://rperezphoto.com/
Victoria Nickerson 
Arvid Logan - http://arvidlogan.tumblr.com/
Alexsandra Star - 
John Ralston - http://john-ralston.tumblr.com/
Samuel Puglia - http://slakron.tumblr.com/
Ryan Maleady - http://ryanmaleady.com/
Annika Zee - https://soundcloud.com/annika_zee/crazy
Mordechai Rubenstein - http://mistermort.com/
Milah Libin - http://milahlibin.tumblr.com/info
M.T.
Ray Martinez - http://exp.nike.com/us/en_us/e/cities/nyc/articles/masters-of-air/spaghetti-boys
Paul Simone 

Eyelove2stare's main focus has always been the beauty that is other people. Our radio show on Know-Wave.com features voice memos of various New York City peoples teling stories, yelling on the phone or talking to someone on the streets, while they are unexpectedly recorded. 

https://soundcloud.com/know-wave/the-fattest-little-baby-show-aug-18th-2015
https://soundcloud.com/know-wave/the-fattest-little-baby-show-aug-26th-2015
https://soundcloud.com/know-wave/the-fattest-little-baby-show-october-14th-2015

This art show is a new creation of what a gallery experience can be like when you eliminate some points of anxiety and insecurities. The art ties into the theme that people are naturally their most beautiful when they feel they are not being watched or recorded. The idea that people can unknowingly create something that can be considered so valuable to someone else... Come expierence this show and support your local art movement!

This art show will feature our newest The Fattest Little Baby show Streaming Live in the room and on know-wave.com friday June 10th at 9pm with interactive instagram zine. Come by and check out the experience we are creating.
